<br>
The early stages of currency have something backing them.  Wether it be a barter system, precious metal/substance.<br>
<br>
For example early american currency used Spanish coins.  They then took these coins and cut them up into bits.  (2 bits for your time ring a bell?).  <br>
<br>
Talens are not using pre-existing currency, or valuable materials to back up the word talen.  In fact the word Talen is just that. A word.<br>
